# Frontend .env.example
#
# Same-origin architecture: the middleware (port 3000) serves the SPA
# statically and proxies /api/* to the backend. All frontend requests
# use relative paths, so no VITE_BACKEND_URL / VITE_MIDDLEWARE_URL are
# needed. Leave this file empty (or delete it) unless adding new
# VITE_-prefixed build-time vars.
